---
title: Mediterranean Double Turkey Burgers with Yogurt Sauce
description: Wholesome and tender turkey patties are bursting with bold flavour! Roast potatoes in halves to save on prep time. Dip the golden-brown nuggets into the cooling yogurt sauce.
